data.Name: One Flew West
data.Bio: One Flew West pertains to two musical artist: 1) a pop punk band from Colorado or 2) a rock band from Toronto 1)Formed in the Summer of 2010 in the small town of Longmont, Colorado, One Flew West has grown from a high school garage band into a full-scale rock machine storming up and down the front range. Now based in Denver, the four-piece has made a lasting mark on the local music scene and look to make that mark on the national scene in the near future. Read more on Last.fm
